<h1>About AdvancedDevSample</h1>

<p>
    AdvancedDevSample is a production-oriented .NET reference project designed to show how to build,
    test, secure, and operate a modern full-stack application with realistic engineering constraints.
</p>

<h2>What this project demonstrates</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Clean Architecture and explicit domain boundaries.</li>
    <li>JWT authentication with refresh token rotation and rate limiting.</li>
    <li>Blazor WebAssembly frontend integrated with a typed API client.</li>
    <li>CI/CD quality gates for testing, coverage, formatting, and security scans.</li>
    <li>Operational basics: logging, Sentry integration, and deployment automation.</li>
</ul>

<p>
    Source code and technical documentation are available on
    <a href="https://github.com/BAYRYO/AdvancedDevSample" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>.
</p>
